definition: Jiayin county in Yichun 伊春市[Yi1 chun1 shi4], Heilongjiang
Jiayin county in Yichun 伊春市[Yi1 chun1 shi4], Heilongjiang

sentences.english: Jiayin dinosaurs belong to China, they have gone out of Heilongjiang.
sentences.chinese: 嘉蔭恐龍屬於中國，它已經走出龍江。

sentences.english: Jiayin dinosaurs belong to the world, they will go out of China.
sentences.chinese: 嘉蔭恐龍屬於屬於世界，它必將走出中國。
